			>
				Connecting Talent to Opportunity, Making Global Success Simple
				and Seamless.
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-lg">
				At Sastika Solutions, we specialize in connecting India’s talent
				with international opportunities, providing end-to-end support
				for visas, work permits, and placements. Our mission is to make
				global career dreams a seamless reality for both job seekers and
				employers.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
